*Zidu* sam čistio pre nekoliko nedelja. (I cleaned the wall a few weeks ago.)

*Zidu* je obojio moj komšija. (My neighbor painted the wall.)

*Zida* su se pojavile pukotine. (Cracks appeared in the wall.)

*Zidu* je morao da obnovim. (I had to renovate the wall.)

*Zidom* sam se opkladio da ću uspeti. (I bet on the wall that I'll succeed.)

*Zidu* se može koristiti kao oslonac. (The wall can be used as a support.)